<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0051402/2026-01-23> a evo:TermVersion ;
    evo:definition "Any apoptotic process in a neuron, the basic cellular unit of nervous tissue. Each neuron consists of a body, an axon, and dendrites. Their purpose is to receive, conduct, and transmit impulses in the nervous system." ;
