<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0071948/2026-01-23> a evo:TermVersion ;
    evo:definition "B cell apoptotic process that occurs upon engagement of either the B cell receptor or CD40. Engagement of either receptor, but not both, leads to expression of fas or related receptors that make the B cell susceptible to fas-ligand mediated death." ;
