<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0140403/2026-01-23> a evo:TermVersion ;
    evo:definition "A process mediated by a molecule secreted by a symbiont that results in the suppression of a host innate immune response. The host is defined as the larger of the organisms involved in a symbiotic interaction." ;
