<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0010421/2025-10-10> a evo:TermVersion ;
    evo:definition "Programmed cell death induced by hydrogen peroxide. Programmed cell death is the cell death resulting from activation of endogenous cellular processes." ;
