<http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/GO_0060058/2025-10-10> a evo:TermVersion ;
    evo:definition "Any process that activates or increases the frequency, rate or extent of cell death by apoptotic process of mammary epithelial cells during mammary gland involution." ;
